                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> The prisoner did not owe me 18<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350511-name-1111" type="witnessName">
