                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1111" type="surname" value="FEARN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1111" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH FEARN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 244.) I apprehended the prisoner—he said he had never had any bad money in his possession.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
